 <div class="slide_content">
  <div class="slide_title">Promoting Alternatives to the Use of Animals in Science</div>
  <p>The Three Rs tenet (Replacement, Reduction and Refinement) guides Canadian scientists on the ethical use of animals in science.</p>
  <p><a href="en_/standards/threer">Find out more</a></p>
 </div>
</div>
				
<div class="slide">
