 <div class="slide_content">
  <div class="slide_title">Delivering Our Mandate with the Help of 2,000 Canadian Volunteers</div>
  <p>The CCAC works with animal health professionals, scientists, representatives of the public and other members of over 225 institutional animal care committees across the country.</p>
  <p><a href="en_/assessment/acc">Find out more</a></p>
